067\" width=700 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809420/extras/3433a2de752bbb763641b602526a7013.webm?t=1703580067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809420/extras/3433a2de752bbb763641b602526a7013.mp4?t=1703580067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>For fans of action, adventure and detective games.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Third person shooter with unique ability to fight against your enemies.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use your stealth and tactical skills, to gather evidence against the corruption.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809420/extras/899edb9b64d6cbf0bd528f680af4da9b.poster.avif?t=1703580067\" width=700 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809420/extras/899edb9b64d6cbf0bd528f680af4da9b.webm?t=1703580067\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1809420/extras/899edb9b64d6cbf0bd528f680af4da9b.mp4?t=1703580067\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Be brave and stand tall, to bring peace in the city Sawhor .</strong>",
